page.title: 22Lifecraft
page.content:
LIFECRAFT

by Pink

I have had the time of my life,

To realise what I'm missing,

What I should be doing,

Not trying to be perfect,

By other people to be a reject,

Finding people to understand,

Not to be pushed around,

To feel safe for the first time,

To be kept away from harm,

I would not change a thing,

What Lifecraft always can bring,

So I am here to stay plus there is no more than I can say,

I always felt like I was blue,

Now I am The Pinkster what are you?


Lifecraft
